world-cup-2014-dream-team
=========================

Choose your World Cup 2014 dream team

PLAYER DB
    https://docs.google.com/a/guardian.co.uk/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AkRR3zKqdlUHdFE5SjJtS3gyUHF3ZEcwYlF0SHgxbkE




MONGO SETUP

    db.users.ensureIndex( { 'guardianID': 1 }, { unique: true });

USER DATA STRUCTURE
    {
        _id:            '001',
        username:       'anom'
        teamSelection:  ['player_id', 'player_id', ...]
    }


MATCH DATA STRUCUTRE
    {
        date:                   'Mon Apr 07 2014 17:21:29 GMT+0100 (BST)'
        user_1_id:              '001',
        user_1_teamSelection:   ['player_id', 'player_id', ...],
        user_1_goals:           2,


        user_2_id:              '002',
        user_2_teamSelection:   ['player_id', 'player_id', ...]
        user_2_goals:           1
    }

